name: Invasion Day Rally Melbourne
description: Join us for the Invasion Day Rally in Melbourne to demand justice and sovereignty for First Nations peoples. Gather at Parliament House and march through the city.

name: Brisbane Invasion Day March
description: Stand in solidarity at the Brisbane Invasion Day March. We will gather to protest the ongoing injustices and call for truth and treaty.
